page.title: 07HAB.BISHOPS WD/KERNE BRIDGE
page.content:
{Bishops Wood In Bishops Wood which is in square 3,we found quite a big garage, it sold caravans but not cars.We found an 18th century house,it was in the shape of a castle's battlements.We also found some modern chalets. A house which is owned by Mr and Mrs Voight,is a Tudor house.
{Kerne Bridge In square 4 which is Kerne Bridge we found one pub which is called Kerne Bridge Inn,it is a Free House. There are two modern houses, one has been built recently.At the back of the pub,there is an old Tudor house, of which the chimney is falling down.
